@node "Source" "Source Code"

   Here's the @{b}complete@{ub} E source code for CheckMouse   ;)

PROC main()

   /*

      State of mouse buttons affects the return code set
      when the program exits.

            No buttons    - RC = 0


         Single buttons ...

            Left button   - RC = 5
            Right button  - RC = 10
            Middle Button - RC = 20

         Combinations ...

            L & R - RC = 15
            L & M - RC = 25
            M & R - RC = 30

            All 3 - RC = 35

   */

ENDPROC Mouse() * 5
@endnode
